<details>
  <summary><b>More info</b></summary>
<br>

- Trees are randomly generated
- 14 custom scraps with some having multiple variants of them
- 1 ambient creature called `Shisha`
- `Shisha` can spawn on every other moons, highly configable custom entity
- Theres a rare chance for it to drop a scrap item called `Unko`
- `Unko` can be red(cheapest) - green - blue(most expensive), scrap item also highly configurable
- When `Shisha` is hit, it will run away from the player, when killed it'll despawn and leave 3 `Unko`s behind
- Custom enemy `Oni` - which is a masked variant
- Custom enemy `Smol Poofer` - which is a Spore Lizard variant
- `Hachiman` is now scannable, and it takes a random pose per round (that moves a little)
- Custom seasons
  - `Snowichi` is on DustCloud weather
  - `Scorchi` is on Eclipsed weather
- `Katana` causes 69 damage if you touch it
- `Katana` has a zone in the middle (that is not as big as the platform) which has 7% chance to trigger an event where it spins around and flies in the air before returning to its original place, its an instant kill which does 690 damage
- If you have `ScarletDevilMansion` interior and it spawns on Seichi, the moon will be desaturized to work well with SDM ^^
- There are custom musics (DMCA free) that play in the background in the morning and in the evening. They are also modified a bit.
- `Spookichi` is unlockable by hitting the pumpking near the main entrance (only `Spookichi` for now, but once halloween is over, the pumpkin will still be available)
  - Daily and evening musics change to fit the theme
  - It has a custom ambience audio, normal Seichi ambience is disabled (Snowichi and Scorchi are still there tho)
  - Red Cauldron has three outcomes: Nothing(just consumes scrap), Flashes player + Spawns rare item, Kills player
  - Green Cauldron also has three outcomes: Nothing, Hurts player for 5 hp + Spawns rare item, Flashes player + Spawns enemy
  - Items that can be dropped in the cauldrons: `Teapot` , `Cup` , `OniMask` , `Vase` , `Uchiwa` , `Naifu` , `Lantern` , `Mortar and Pestle` , `Unko`
- You can stack different versions of the moon - for example `Scorchi` + `SDM-SeichiPatch` + `Spookichi` if you go to Seichi on eclipsed weather with SDM interior picked and you click on the pumpkin
- `Mailbox` either delivers a death sentence or an invitation to one of two dimensions, the rubber room - you have one way out -> PANIC!, or  the dojo for an announcement
- <b>Seichi has three configs, LethalCompanySeichi.cfg, LethalCompanyShisha.cfg, Seichi.cfg (last one is not accessible in lethalconfig but in modmanager)</b>

- This is a bit outdated, but mostly true, Shisha though is going to be a seperate mod and for the wedding feature theres a secret config under the name of FaithSecretRoom/Funny


</details>

